OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FCampaigners will have to wait until
OL,8,Fthe end of the week to find out if
OL,9,Ftheir legal fight against a
OL,10,Fcontroversial migrant camp can proceed.
OL,12,FFollowing a day of arguments at the
OL,13,FHigh Court, the judge confirmed he
OL,14,Fwould take time to consider the facts
OL,15,Fbefore delivering his decision on
OL,16,FFriday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
