CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FThe residents' group, Crowborough
OL,8,FShield, is seeking a judicial review
OL,9,Finto the Home Office's decision to
OL,10,Fhouse hundreds of asylum seekers at a
OL,11,Fformer army training camp in East
OL,12,FSussex.
OL,14,FWATCH: Lead campaigner Kim Bailey
OL,15,Fexplains why she's "not disappointed"
OL,16,Fby the judge's delay, as Crowborough
OL,17,FShield faces a 48-hour wait for the
OL,18,Ffinal decision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FWhile the group had hoped for a
OL,8,Fverdict today, lead campaigner Kim
OL,9,FBailey remained optimistic outside the
OL,10,Fcourt.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian after the
OL,13,Fhearing, Kim Bailey said that despite
OL,14,Fthe delay, she felt the group had put
OL,15,Fforward their best possible case.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,F"I think we put forward a really good
OL,8,Fargument," Ms. Bailey said. "The fact
OL,9,Fit went on a lot longer than expected
OL,10,Fshows the judge was considering the
OL,11,Ffacts in detail. It's not a bad thing;
OL,12,Fit means he's taken on board every
OL,13,Fpoint that was made."
OL,15,FWATCH: "They are representing the
OL,16,Fmajority view" ` Nusrat Ghani MP
OL,17,Fjoined campaigners at the High Court
OL,18,Fthis morning as they seek a judicial
OL,19,Freview against the Home Office
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FThe court heard that the legal
OL,8,Fchallenge, funded by more than
OL,9,F#100,000 in local donations, is based
OL,10,Fon claims that the Home Office acted
OL,11,Funlawfully.
OL,13,FCampaigners argue there was inadequate
OL,14,Fpublic consultation and that the
OL,15,Fimpact of housing hundreds of men in a
OL,16,Frural area was not properly assessed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FDespite the campaigners' confidence,
OL,8,Fthe judge indicated that the
OL,9,Fapplication may be flawed. The court's
OL,10,Fconcerns centre on the fact that the
OL,11,Flegal challenge relies heavily on Home
OL,12,FOffice decision-making prior to
OL,13,FJanuary 21 - the key date when the
OL,14,Ffirst migrants were moved onto the
OL,15,Fsite.
OL,17,FNusrat Ghani, MP for Sussex and Weald,
OL,18,Fwas also at the court to support the
OL,19,Fresidents. She has previously slammed
OL,20,Fthe "zero consultation" provided by
OL,21,Fthe government.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,F"The Home Office have never been able
OL,8,Fto share the assessment of how the
OL,9,Fsite is safe, legal, compliant or even
OL,10,Fshown us any long-term plans," Ms.
OL,11,FGhani told ITV Meridian this morning.
OL,13,FThe Home Office argues that the site
OL,14,Fis a vital part of its strategy to
OL,15,Freduce the #9 million-a-day cost of
OL,16,Fhousing asylum seekers in hotels.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FThe site began housing its first
OL,8,Fresidents in late January, which
OL,9,Fsparked a march of thousands through
OL,10,Fthe streets in what was described as
OL,11,Fthe "loudest protest yet". Local
OL,12,Fcampaign groups argue the rural
OL,13,Flocation lacks the necessary
OL,14,Finfrastructure and public services to
OL,15,Fsupport the influx of residents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FThe tension in the town reached a
OL,8,Fboiling point last month, with Sussex
OL,9,FPolice making several arrests
OL,10,Ffollowing reports of disorder outside
OL,11,Fthe barracks. While recent marches
OL,12,Fhave remained largely peaceful, a
OL,13,Fheavy police presence remains a common
OL,14,Fsight in the area.
OL,16,FThe camp now holds an estimated 100
OL,17,Fpeople and is expected to eventually
OL,18,Fhouse up to 600 single men.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FGovernment officials maintain that the
OL,8,Fsite is "basic and safe," featuring 24/
OL,9,F7 security and dedicated on-site
OL,10,Fhealthcare to minimize the impact on
OL,11,Flocal Crowborough services.
OL,13,FHowever, campaigners have challenged
OL,14,Fthe "emergency" status used by the
OL,15,Fgovernment to bypass the standard
OL,16,Fplanning process.
OL,18,FThe judge is expected to deliver their
OL,19,Ffinal decision on whether to allow a
OL,20,Ffull judicial review at the High Court
OL,21,Fon Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772204161
OL,3,CCrowborough migrant camp: Judge delays
OL,4,Cdecision on legal challenge until
OL,5,CFriday
OL,7,FIf successful, the move could lead to
OL,8,Fa full trial and a potential halt to
OL,9,Fthe camp's operations. If the judge
OL,10,Frules in favour of the Home Office,
OL,11,Fthe government will likely continue
OL,12,Fscaling up the number of residents at
OL,13,Fthe site toward its full capacity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
